AraSenti Lexicon
-----------------------


- Read data as follows (in Python):
import pandas as pd
data= pd.read_csv('AraSentiLexiconV1.0.csv')

Or read the original data text file (AraSentiLexiconV1.0.) but make sure to set the encoding to (windows-1256).

